prodNameC: 亞培設計師B型利鈉胜肽檢驗試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
ARCHITECT Reagent Kit：
MICROPARTICLES
Anti-BNP (Mouse, Monoclonal) coated microparticles in TRIS buffer with protein (bovine, mouse) stabilizers.

CONJUGATE
Anti-BNP (Mouse, Monoclonal) acridinium-labeled conjugate in MES buffer with protein (bovine) stabilizers. Minimum concentration：0.1μg/mL. 

SPECIMEN DILUENT
containing TRIS buffer with protein (bovine) stabilizers.

ARCHITECT BNP Calibrators：
Calibrator A is Acetate buffer with protein (bovine) stabilizers. Calibrators B-F contain BNP in Acetate buffer with protein (bovine) stabilizers.
ARCHITECT BNP Controls： 
Containing BNP in Acetate buffer with protein (bovine) stabilizers.
